you're talking about Africa,

00:02:47.510 --> 00:02:51.730
the Middle East, Asia,
Pakistan, India, Indonesia,

00:02:51.730 --> 00:02:53.860
Central Asia, even Europe.

00:02:53.860 --> 00:02:56.890
