We've heard the professors talking
about the clash of civilizations.

01:48:47.310 --> 01:48:50.800
We are seeing in some ways,
whether we agree or not,

01:48:50.800 --> 01:48:53.430
a clash of civilizations
taking place.

01:48:53.430 --> 01:48:55.320
It is happening and
there's no reason

