01:50:05.510 --> 01:50:10.150 position:56%
the first really great sociologist
I think it's fair to say, historian,

01:50:10.150 --> 01:50:13.280
of course, great historian
of the Berbers.

01:50:13.280 --> 01:50:19.010
But the first great sociological
theorist of the movement

01:50:19.010 --> 01:50:23.460
of peoples in Northern Africa.

01:50:23.460 --> 01:50:27.830
