02:11:07.960 --> 02:11:15.830
Let me just, before I introduce
Amir Al-Islam, let me just try

02:11:15.830 --> 02:11:21.920 position:56%
to briefly pull together a couple of
the threads that we've heard so far,

02:11:21.920 --> 02:11:23.700
because Professor Hunwick,

02:11:23.700 --> 02:11:30.130
by emphasizing the Islamic
learned tradition in Timbuktu,

02:11:30.130 --> 02:11:34.950
which of course came
down from North Africa,

02:11:34.950 --> 02:11:39.360
