02:14:50.600 --> 02:14:55.460
ideas, perspectives,
and research on Islam

02:14:55.460 --> 02:14:58.780 position:56%
and the African American experience.

02:14:58.780 --> 02:15:05.080
I have -- we tried to in the
beginning get the order switched,

02:15:05.080 --> 02:15:07.720
because Akbar Ahmed
is one of my mentors,

02:15:07.720 --> 02:15:10.800
a person that I read and study.

02:15:10.800 --> 02:15:13.930 position:56%
And I thought that he -- it would be
