02:26:16.810 --> 02:26:21.380
Now finally, let me say that
in spite of the difficulties,

02:26:21.380 --> 02:26:23.930
in spite of the suffering,
in spite of the indignities,

02:26:23.930 --> 02:26:26.960
in spite of the challenge, of
