02:29:57.620 --> 02:30:00.920 position:56%
We're going to create an environment
that embraces difference,

02:30:00.920 --> 02:30:06.300
that transforms us, that allows us
to create collectively an America

02:30:06.300 --> 02:30:10.870
that we envision, that I
envision, that Dr. King envisioned,

02:30:10.870 --> 02:30:14.660
that all of us would like to
see, that embraces all of us

02:30:14.660 --> 02:30:15.990
and celebrates our difference.

02:30:15.990 --> 02:30:18.430
